WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 23]

01:17.470 --> 01:21.420
You're the maid who took Jingwu away!

01:24.160 --> 01:26.220
I'm Miaoqing. Greetings, Your Ladyship.

01:28.910 --> 01:31.860
Insulting nobility is punishable by death.

01:32.880 --> 01:33.860
Drag her off and flog her to death.

01:33.880 --> 01:34.290
- Yes. - Yes.

01:34.310 --> 01:34.860
Wait!

01:40.080 --> 01:40.620
Tongzhou.

01:44.830 --> 01:45.500
Everyone leave.

01:46.310 --> 01:46.780
- Yes. - Yes.

01:51.240 --> 01:51.810
Tongzhou.

01:52.470 --> 01:54.140
This lowly maid has no sense of rank.

01:54.520 --> 01:55.530
Why keep her around?

01:57.550 --> 01:58.530
Without her,

01:59.110 --> 02:01.370
Jingwu would've fallen into Zong Quan's hands too.

02:08.360 --> 02:10.090
Miaoqing, take the Crown Prince away.

02:11.030 --> 02:12.620
Yes, Your Highness.

02:23.990 --> 02:24.570
Tongzhou.

02:26.710 --> 02:27.410
Tongzhou.

02:28.110 --> 02:29.740
Look.

02:30.590 --> 02:31.940
Aren't these Twin Orbs beautiful?

02:35.900 --> 02:39.060
I've waited so long for this day.

02:39.360 --> 02:41.530
Do you remember when I first came to Duantu?

02:41.960 --> 02:43.940
You taught me calligraphy at Orchid Pavilion

02:44.480 --> 02:45.850
and said my writing was nice.

02:46.270 --> 02:49.740
You said I'd meet a good man

02:50.110 --> 02:50.970
and be happy forever.

02:53.760 --> 02:54.340
Tongzhou,

02:54.990 --> 02:56.940
you're the only man I've ever wanted.

02:57.800 --> 02:59.370
These Twin Orbs were left by my parents.

03:00.710 --> 03:02.780
In a few days, we'll be wed.

03:03.430 --> 03:04.090
I've decided.

03:04.670 --> 03:08.130
One orb will go on my crown.

03:08.360 --> 03:09.570
As for the other, I can...

03:09.590 --> 03:10.900
The Crown Prince ascends in three days.

03:13.150 --> 03:14.180
You want to be the Empress?

03:15.360 --> 03:17.530
I doubt Tonghe would approve from the grave.

03:20.900 --> 03:22.060
Jingwu is ascending the throne?

03:23.320 --> 03:24.570
Why not you, Tongzhou?

03:31.110 --> 03:32.250
It's okay.

03:32.960 --> 03:34.740
It's perfectly fine if you don't want to be

03:35.150 --> 03:36.970
the Emperor. I don't want to be the Empress.

03:37.480 --> 03:38.740
Just being with you

03:39.080 --> 03:40.130
is enough for me.

03:44.320 --> 03:44.850
Lanya.

03:46.760 --> 03:48.410
When did you become so foolish?

03:51.390 --> 03:53.300
A blood debt can only be paid with blood.

03:54.150 --> 03:55.780
Killing you wouldn't quench my hatred.

03:58.270 --> 03:59.300
How could I ever marry you?

04:00.390 --> 04:00.780
Tong...

04:01.800 --> 04:02.250
Tong...

04:02.670 --> 04:03.220
Tongzhou.

04:05.390 --> 04:07.370
But... but you said

04:08.040 --> 04:09.300
once Zong Quan was dead,

04:10.110 --> 04:11.850
everything from the past would be forgotten.

04:13.200 --> 04:14.690
And you know

04:15.710 --> 04:17.300
I...

04:17.520 --> 04:18.460
I love you.

04:18.670 --> 04:19.250
- Shut up! - For...

04:21.640 --> 04:23.370
All you care about is yourself!

04:23.790 --> 04:26.250
No, Tongzhou. That's not true.

04:27.320 --> 04:29.060
After your parents died for the kingdom,

04:30.590 --> 04:33.180
Tonghe and I always treated you like a sister.

04:34.000 --> 04:35.370
We showered you with care. But you?

04:35.960 --> 04:37.620
For your selfish gain,

04:37.640 --> 04:39.860
you betrayed the Yue State and killed my uncle.

04:40.230 --> 04:42.100
No. No.

04:42.120 --> 04:44.130
You're utterly disgusting.

04:44.830 --> 04:46.890
Tongzhou! No. Tongzhou.

04:47.390 --> 04:49.690
Have you forgotten? The Heartbound Gu.

04:50.830 --> 04:53.570
Don't forget, you have the Heartbound Gu inside you.

04:53.880 --> 04:55.860
You are stuck with me for life.

04:56.390 --> 04:57.370
If you didn't love me,

04:57.590 --> 04:59.570
why... why would you have taken the Heartbound Gu,

04:59.590 --> 05:00.180
right?

05:00.830 --> 05:01.450
Tongzhou.

05:02.270 --> 05:02.980
Am I right?

05:03.000 --> 05:03.540
Lanya.

05:04.790 --> 05:06.570
There's a heart-protecting herb from Miaojiang

05:07.270 --> 05:09.010
that can shield one's heart meridians

05:09.030 --> 05:10.100
when the gu burns.

05:10.120 --> 05:10.890
Didn't you know?

05:24.960 --> 05:26.690
Tongzhou. No.

05:27.760 --> 05:28.690
You'll die.

05:29.440 --> 05:31.010
I'd rather burn myself

05:33.030 --> 05:34.540
than let you have your way.

05:34.560 --> 05:36.100
I'll die too! No!

05:38.960 --> 05:40.060
Don't, Tongzhou!

05:43.830 --> 05:44.690
Tongzhou.

05:46.030 --> 05:47.010
Tongzhou.

05:50.710 --> 05:51.690
Does that hurt?

05:53.960 --> 05:55.860
This isn't even a fraction

05:57.080 --> 05:59.130
of what you've done!

06:01.710 --> 06:02.570
Tongzhou...

06:08.470 --> 06:11.740
Are you really going to kill me, Tongzhou?

06:38.710 --> 06:44.690
"What can I give to my beloved?"

06:48.080 --> 06:56.940
"Twin Orbs, hanging

07:04.640 --> 07:05.210
together."

07:35.230 --> 07:35.940
No.

07:51.560 --> 07:52.100
Who's there?

07:52.440 --> 07:52.980
Your Highness.

07:53.680 --> 07:54.620
It's me, Miaoqing.

07:56.590 --> 07:57.130
Your Highness.

08:05.710 --> 08:06.540
Why are you here?

08:09.960 --> 08:13.180
Your Highness, did you have a nightmare?

08:19.030 --> 08:22.100
Dreams aren't real. Don't take them to heart.

08:27.640 --> 08:29.060
They also said dreams weren't real.

08:31.080 --> 08:32.330
But the Yue State fell.

08:33.590 --> 08:36.900
Tonghe was killed. My uncle died horribly.

08:39.590 --> 08:41.060
All of it came true.

08:42.160 --> 08:42.940
No.

08:45.040 --> 08:46.060
That's all in the past.

08:47.080 --> 08:48.450
Things will get better.

08:51.630 --> 08:55.300
No. They won't get better.

08:55.870 --> 08:57.060
They all left me.

08:58.470 --> 08:59.730
I'm the only one left.

09:01.160 --> 09:02.380
All alone.

09:05.470 --> 09:07.780
Your Highness, you're not alone.

09:09.590 --> 09:11.140
I'll always be by your side.

09:27.320 --> 09:29.330
Lu and I are heading back to Wanxian Sect to report.

09:29.920 --> 09:30.970
Next time we meet,

09:31.320 --> 09:33.060
it'll probably be when the Sea Calamity comes.

09:37.990 --> 09:40.020
Tongzhou, I have to go too.

09:40.920 --> 09:43.020
My master and seniors at Zhuiyu Peak are waiting for news.

09:43.630 --> 09:44.260
Besides,

09:44.630 --> 09:45.940
I still need to find my old master.

09:46.200 --> 09:47.140
I really shouldn't stay any longer.

09:47.470 --> 09:48.610
Lifei, stay a few more days.

09:48.800 --> 09:49.940
I can help you find your master.

09:50.710 --> 09:51.810
Lifei has decided to leave.

09:52.040 --> 09:53.810
We should respect her choice.

09:53.990 --> 09:54.490
You...

09:59.710 --> 10:01.260
Ji Tongzhou, are you insane?

10:04.060 --> 10:05.900
Tongzhou, what are you doing?

10:13.230 --> 10:14.540
Is this the mark of demonic possession?

10:22.590 --> 10:23.610
Brahma's Net?

10:38.300 --> 10:41.690
You ignorant fools! Hand over the Divine Tree!

10:50.510 --> 10:51.300
Elder Cuixuan,

10:51.980 --> 10:53.380
we just finished driving out the Wugou army.

10:54.060 --> 10:55.330
We don't know anything about any Divine Tree.

10:55.980 --> 10:58.660
The night before last, the Divine Tree's aura surged straight into the sky.

10:59.180 --> 11:01.970
And the source of that aura was right here.

11:08.220 --> 11:11.850
Back at Chufeng Academy, the Divine Tree's aura also appeared.

11:13.060 --> 11:15.610
All of this is connected to you people.

11:16.340 --> 11:18.490
Today, I'll personally find out

11:19.230 --> 11:21.610
where the Divine Tree is!

11:41.180 --> 11:41.970
Sir,

11:42.180 --> 11:43.900
Zong Quan killed Elder Xuanshan

11:43.990 --> 11:45.330
and slaughtered everyone in Xingzheng Hall.

11:46.460 --> 11:48.180
We nearly lost our lives

11:48.460 --> 11:49.690
defeating him.

11:50.680 --> 11:51.570
Now you're here

11:51.980 --> 11:53.090
demanding some Divine Tree

11:53.830 --> 11:55.810
instead of healing us.

11:56.680 --> 11:58.570
You're leaving us no way out.

12:01.510 --> 12:02.490
Elder Cuixuan!

12:04.230 --> 12:05.730
Where were you when the Yue State fell

12:06.590 --> 12:09.180
and Xingzheng Hall was wiped out?

12:09.820 --> 12:11.450
Where was Wuyue Court

12:11.680 --> 12:12.900
when we fought Zong Quan?

12:13.630 --> 12:16.300
Compared to the calamity that threatens to ruin the Central Plains,

12:17.100 --> 12:19.940
the fate of one kingdom means nothing.

12:20.470 --> 12:21.610
As for Zong Quan,

12:21.980 --> 12:24.490
he's fallen to demonic arts and has abandoned the immortal path.

12:24.870 --> 12:26.660
He has nothing to do with Wuyue Court!

12:27.510 --> 12:29.260
I suggest you see reason

12:29.630 --> 12:31.060
and hand over the Divine Tree.

12:31.830 --> 12:33.970
No more useless words.

12:34.320 --> 12:36.260
We really don't know where the Divine Tree is.

12:36.440 --> 12:37.260
What can we give you?

12:43.470 --> 12:44.780
You're a revered master of an immortal sect.

12:45.110 --> 12:46.450
Yet you hound disciples over something

12:46.750 --> 12:47.540
that may not even exist.

12:48.630 --> 12:49.940
Do you not fear losing the hearts of your people?

12:52.440 --> 12:53.570
There is no Divine Tree here.

12:54.040 --> 12:56.810
If Wuyue Court insists on bullying the weak,

12:57.110 --> 12:59.940
I will fight you to the death!

13:00.350 --> 13:04.610
Fight to the death!

13:07.960 --> 13:09.210
Ignorant fools.

13:10.440 --> 13:11.730
With you people?

13:16.700 --> 13:17.300
Cuixuan,

13:17.960 --> 13:20.570
we came here to find the Divine Tree,

13:20.870 --> 13:21.850
not to fight.

13:22.510 --> 13:23.380
Isn't that right?

13:25.540 --> 13:29.020
Since Zong Quan once occupied this place,

13:29.630 --> 13:30.940
could he have hidden

13:31.160 --> 13:33.570
the Divine Tree somewhere here?

13:35.440 --> 13:36.300
Have you done

13:36.320 --> 13:38.730
a thorough search?

13:40.280 --> 13:40.900
Sir,

13:41.440 --> 13:42.570
we've been busy cleaning up the mess,

13:42.830 --> 13:43.610
and we're all wounded.

13:44.080 --> 13:44.970
We haven't done a full search yet.

13:45.540 --> 13:48.020
See? There are still gaps.

13:52.470 --> 13:55.090
Cuixuan, the Sea Sect has just settled down.

13:55.350 --> 13:57.540
We can't afford more conflict within the Mountain Sect.

13:58.230 --> 14:00.260
If we let our fellow cultivators down,

14:00.510 --> 14:02.970
the demons will take advantage.

14:03.960 --> 14:06.970
Ji Tongzhou just lost his entire family.

14:07.630 --> 14:09.090
It's understandable

14:09.200 --> 14:10.380
he spoke out of turn.

14:11.350 --> 14:12.380
How about this?

14:12.710 --> 14:14.420
Let's give the young ones some time

14:15.040 --> 14:17.420
to find the Divine Tree.

14:18.440 --> 14:19.210
Is that acceptable?

14:26.350 --> 14:27.450
Cuixuan, you're wise.

14:29.560 --> 14:33.060
The Divine Tree concerns the safety of the Central Plains.

14:33.750 --> 14:36.140
Everyone here bears responsibility!

14:37.280 --> 14:39.180
I'll give you twenty-four hours...

14:46.110 --> 14:47.140
Twelve hours.

14:48.110 --> 14:49.380
You have twelve hours

14:49.960 --> 14:50.970
to hand over the Divine Tree!

14:51.350 --> 14:54.380
Or I'll take matters into my own hands!

15:10.160 --> 15:13.330
Alright. Your life isn't in danger,

15:13.590 --> 15:14.850
but your energy is unstable.

15:14.990 --> 15:17.140
You need to rest well during this time.

15:19.200 --> 15:20.020
Master,

15:21.830 --> 15:24.900
- my spirit aura...
- I don't want to hear it.

15:25.990 --> 15:28.210
And I don't want to know.

15:29.230 --> 15:32.260
All I know is you're my disciple.

15:35.470 --> 15:37.090
So I have to say something.

15:37.630 --> 15:39.060
You've got some nerve.

15:39.350 --> 15:40.210
With your skill level,

15:40.230 --> 15:42.450
how could you go head-to-head with Zong Quan?

15:42.990 --> 15:44.020
Silly girl.

15:44.960 --> 15:46.690
Well, none of you sect elders

15:46.710 --> 15:47.610
lifted a finger.

15:48.560 --> 15:50.380
I was just following your teachings

15:50.400 --> 15:52.060
to be discerning and sacrifice myself for what's right.

15:52.230 --> 15:53.570
I wasn't about to stand by

15:53.590 --> 15:54.610
and do nothing like you.

15:56.750 --> 15:59.140
We weren't standing by.

15:59.870 --> 16:01.210
The immortal sects aren't supposed to

16:01.230 --> 16:03.180
interfere in disputes between kingdoms.

16:04.110 --> 16:04.690
And

16:05.560 --> 16:07.610
when exactly did I teach you to sacrifice yourself?

16:07.710 --> 16:10.090
I've always taught you to stay alive.

16:11.080 --> 16:12.730
I'm doing pretty well at that.

16:21.960 --> 16:22.420
Sir.

16:28.320 --> 16:29.180
You're just in time.

16:29.750 --> 16:30.850
I was going to find you.

16:31.750 --> 16:33.090
They say you're exceptionally gifted.

16:33.110 --> 16:34.330
Where exactly is this gift of yours?

16:34.960 --> 16:36.330
You've had my disciple for three months.

16:36.440 --> 16:37.570
Look at her now.

16:37.990 --> 16:38.850
She's broken and battered.

16:38.870 --> 16:40.810
Can you even protect anyone?

16:50.350 --> 16:51.140
Sir, you're right.

16:54.200 --> 16:56.420
I didn't protect her well.

17:01.870 --> 17:05.450
Is this the same defiant brat

17:05.470 --> 17:07.330
Guangwei used to complain about?

17:13.750 --> 17:14.860
I trained him.

17:15.960 --> 17:16.690
Impressive, right?

17:32.100 --> 17:33.940
Why do I feel so out of place

17:33.960 --> 17:35.140
and unwanted?

17:35.990 --> 17:37.900
So awkward. I'm leaving.

17:42.790 --> 17:43.770
Sir, let me see you out.

18:06.880 --> 18:08.010
In six hours,

18:08.160 --> 18:10.660
at first light, when the sun and moon meet,

18:10.990 --> 18:11.660
the Brahma's Net

18:11.680 --> 18:13.690
will be at its weakest.

18:14.160 --> 18:16.380
I'll do everything I can to hold Cuixuan off.

18:18.960 --> 18:19.730
What do you mean?

18:20.400 --> 18:21.100
Take her away.

18:24.400 --> 18:25.450
Go far away.

18:26.710 --> 18:28.530
Never return to Wuyue Court.

18:30.440 --> 18:30.940
But...

18:41.270 --> 18:41.970
Sir.

18:50.310 --> 18:51.690
If we don't find the Divine Tree,

18:51.960 --> 18:53.820
Cuixuan won't let this go.

18:56.200 --> 18:57.860
Lu, have you ever seen the Divine Tree?

18:58.880 --> 19:01.900
Legend says it was born from the spirit energy of heaven and earth

19:02.600 --> 19:03.860
and grows on Divine Tree Island.

19:05.270 --> 19:06.580
But after the last Sea Calamity,

19:07.070 --> 19:07.970
it vanished without a trace.

19:09.960 --> 19:11.210
It hasn't been seen in centuries?

19:13.160 --> 19:14.690
Then who knows where the Divine Tree is?

19:15.160 --> 19:16.730
He's clearly making things impossible.

19:17.400 --> 19:18.660
The Yue State just ended one war,

19:19.710 --> 19:21.140
and now we're stuck with this mess.

19:21.470 --> 19:22.380
Sorry to drag everyone into this.

19:25.200 --> 19:25.860
Tongzhou.

19:27.880 --> 19:28.380
Here.

19:29.070 --> 19:30.490
I had some snacks made.

19:30.790 --> 19:31.340
Try some.

19:33.960 --> 19:34.380
Here.

19:35.710 --> 19:36.340
Tongzhou.

19:36.990 --> 19:38.380
Once the twelve hours are up,

19:38.550 --> 19:39.620
what's your plan?

19:43.680 --> 19:45.770
I've already had Mingli scour the entire area.

19:46.600 --> 19:47.580
If we find it, we find it.

19:48.400 --> 19:49.290
If not,

19:51.340 --> 19:52.420
I'll take full responsibility.

19:56.070 --> 19:56.900
You all

19:57.710 --> 19:58.820
risked your lives to help me.

19:59.400 --> 20:01.450
No matter what, I'll make sure you're all safe.

20:02.790 --> 20:04.290
I came here to protect you.

20:04.440 --> 20:05.530
How could I let you face this alone?

20:06.200 --> 20:08.450
If it comes to it, we'll fight Cuixuan.

20:08.880 --> 20:09.770
We might not lose.

20:13.230 --> 20:15.010
Lu, as for you...

20:16.200 --> 20:18.210
Gelin's friends are my friends.

20:37.030 --> 20:37.970
Unless the barrier is lifted,

20:38.200 --> 20:39.820
everyone inside the imperial palace is trapped.

20:40.510 --> 20:41.820
No one else should be dragged into this.

20:42.400 --> 20:43.290
When the barrier weakens,

20:44.100 --> 20:45.010
I'll draw Cuixuan away.

20:45.640 --> 20:46.770
You take Lifei and get out.

20:47.600 --> 20:48.140
No.

20:50.340 --> 20:51.210
You make it sound simple.

20:52.100 --> 20:53.210
Cuixuan is cunning and sly.

20:53.270 --> 20:54.180
How will you draw him away?

21:00.680 --> 21:02.010
Cuixuan wants the Divine Tree.

21:05.100 --> 21:05.860
Actually, the Divine Tree...

21:05.880 --> 21:07.050
The Divine Tree is on me.

21:25.510 --> 21:27.530
This is... the Divine Tree?

21:28.160 --> 21:28.770
Where did you get it?

21:30.160 --> 21:31.010
From the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff.

21:33.960 --> 21:35.530
I thought you destroyed it.

21:36.880 --> 21:39.620
At the time, I sensed its unusual spirit energy

21:40.100 --> 21:41.180
and brought it back to study.

21:42.840 --> 21:43.940
It was only when Cuixuan came

21:44.470 --> 21:46.770
that I realized it was actually the Divine Tree.

21:50.640 --> 21:52.140
Would handing it over to Cuixuan

21:53.100 --> 21:54.380
draw him away?

22:00.400 --> 22:01.140
Absolutely not.

22:02.880 --> 22:04.900
That night, the Divine Tree's aura surged straight into the sky.

22:05.400 --> 22:06.530
He'll never believe it came

22:07.030 --> 22:08.210
from just a piece of bone.

22:08.710 --> 22:11.420
We need to find a way to end this once and for all.

22:12.710 --> 22:14.100
Then we'll make it impossible to prove.

22:14.710 --> 22:16.010
Blame it all on Zong Quan!

22:17.030 --> 22:17.940
I was thinking the same thing.

22:18.960 --> 22:20.210
We could use the demonic energy

22:20.920 --> 22:21.940
on the Altar of Heaven.

22:27.230 --> 22:29.900
But how do we make it impossible to prove?

22:36.790 --> 22:39.210
I'll disguise myself as Lifei. You play the demon.

22:41.230 --> 22:41.940
Stop right there.

22:42.340 --> 22:43.450
Do you think he's blind?

22:47.100 --> 22:49.340
I'm warning you two, don't take any risks.

22:50.470 --> 22:51.580
Let me think of something else.

23:00.710 --> 23:02.100
Can't go by air.

23:04.160 --> 23:05.010
What about underground?

23:23.340 --> 23:24.010
Water.

23:25.920 --> 23:27.010
What about going by water?

23:54.840 --> 23:55.730
What are you doing here?

23:58.400 --> 24:00.770
Your Highness, I want to share your burden.

24:02.070 --> 24:03.730
You're just a maid. What can you do?

24:04.230 --> 24:05.100
Take care of yourself.

24:08.030 --> 24:10.660
The late emperor and Elder Xuanshanzi entrusted you with everything.

24:10.960 --> 24:12.210
You must not put yourself in danger

24:12.640 --> 24:13.690
and worry the Crown Prince.

24:14.840 --> 24:17.530
I would do anything for you,

24:18.880 --> 24:19.820
without a single regret.

24:21.340 --> 24:22.420
I know your loyalty.

24:22.710 --> 24:24.050
But this time, you can't help.

24:24.470 --> 24:25.530
If we don't try,

24:26.440 --> 24:27.900
how do we know a way won't open up?

24:29.400 --> 24:30.010
Your Highness,

24:30.750 --> 24:33.380
just let me try.

24:44.310 --> 24:45.490
Time is running out.

24:46.440 --> 24:47.770
Hand over the Divine Tree now,

24:48.310 --> 24:51.210
or don't blame me for resorting to force!

24:52.750 --> 24:53.580
Sir,

24:54.160 --> 24:55.530
I don't know where the Divine Tree is.

24:55.790 --> 24:56.940
Even if it exists,

24:57.310 --> 24:58.900
it must be with the demons.

25:00.550 --> 25:01.900
Why are you pushing us so hard?

25:19.030 --> 25:20.380
The Divine Tree's aura.

25:53.920 --> 25:54.580
Close your eyes.

25:55.750 --> 25:56.250
Go!

25:57.200 --> 25:57.820
Don't run!

26:29.990 --> 26:31.490
It really is the Divine Tree.

26:43.920 --> 26:46.140
If you hadn't used the Xuanhua Sacred Fire,

26:46.470 --> 26:48.290
the Divine Tree wouldn't have been destroyed!

26:51.160 --> 26:52.900
You're the one who scared them off.

26:53.510 --> 26:55.580
That black-clad demon must be Zong Quan's accomplice!

26:58.510 --> 27:00.490
Sir, if you hadn't been pushing so hard,

27:00.960 --> 27:01.940
Tongzhou would've found

27:01.960 --> 27:03.690
the Divine Tree that Zong Quan hid in the palace.

27:04.200 --> 27:05.050
Now we have nothing.

27:05.340 --> 27:05.860
Outrageous!

27:08.440 --> 27:09.180
Cuixuan.

27:09.790 --> 27:11.970
I think Zong Quan's situation is complicated.

27:12.200 --> 27:13.970
He's practicing evil arts now

27:14.200 --> 27:16.250
and has ties to the Divine Tree.

27:17.030 --> 27:17.730
What a pity

27:17.880 --> 27:18.450
we only got

27:18.470 --> 27:20.490
a fragment of the Divine Tree.

27:21.160 --> 27:22.490
Do you think a mere fragment

27:22.510 --> 27:25.420
has weaker spirit energy than the whole thing?

27:26.340 --> 27:27.690
Even if it's just a fragment,

27:28.340 --> 27:30.010
I need to refine it as soon as possible.

27:39.640 --> 27:41.730
Where are Jiang Lifei and Lei Xiuyuan?

27:47.750 --> 27:48.820
Jiang hasn't healed from her injuries.

27:49.440 --> 27:51.050
Lei has been looking after her.

27:52.160 --> 27:52.900
How convenient.

27:53.470 --> 27:54.900
The moment a demon spy appeared,

27:55.200 --> 27:56.820
those two vanished.

27:57.790 --> 27:59.530
Sir, with you and Elder Chongyi here,

27:59.840 --> 28:01.580
we wouldn't dare overstep.

28:02.200 --> 28:04.010
We don't want to give anyone more reason to talk.

28:04.880 --> 28:06.580
Besides, we weren't even there when the demon was chased.

28:08.200 --> 28:11.730
Right. Lifei was badly hurt this time.

28:12.790 --> 28:13.730
Perfect.

28:14.160 --> 28:15.490
I'll go see

28:16.100 --> 28:17.620
just how badly hurt she is.

28:23.600 --> 28:24.180
Mas...

28:31.510 --> 28:33.970
Lifei, I brought Elder Cuixuan to see you.

28:38.710 --> 28:39.660
Maybe we should skip it?

28:40.100 --> 28:40.860
Out of my way!

29:01.070 --> 29:02.420
How is she? Is she alri...?

29:06.510 --> 29:07.530
Master.

29:11.200 --> 29:12.690
What are you two doing?

29:21.600 --> 29:24.940
Sir, they've been close since their academy days.

29:25.840 --> 29:28.380
They're in love. Couldn't help themselves.

29:29.070 --> 29:29.860
It's a good thing!

29:30.200 --> 29:31.660
Good thing, my foot!

29:32.440 --> 29:33.730
This brings shame to our sect!

29:37.990 --> 29:39.290
Never expected Mountain Sect disciples

29:40.120 --> 29:41.530
to be so passionate.

29:42.230 --> 29:43.620
Admirable.

29:44.310 --> 29:46.530
Enough! Don't make things worse.

29:50.790 --> 29:53.900
No wonder the three of them have such tangled ties.

29:54.640 --> 29:56.010
The Divine Tree's spirit aura has weakened.

29:56.200 --> 29:57.820
I need to return and refine it.

29:59.920 --> 30:01.820
All of you, go back.

30:02.120 --> 30:03.730
We've had enough embarrassment today.

30:04.710 --> 30:05.490
Please.

30:06.120 --> 30:07.860
Save some face for Zhuiyu Peak.

30:08.750 --> 30:10.180
Just go back. Alright?

30:12.360 --> 30:13.970
A fine disciple you have.

30:16.990 --> 30:18.900
I'll leave her to you.

30:37.400 --> 30:38.340
Pack up.

30:39.440 --> 30:41.050
Go back to where you belong.

30:48.230 --> 30:49.820
Exactly. There's always time.

30:50.160 --> 30:50.900
The elders...

30:51.360 --> 30:52.730
The elders already know anyway.

31:01.030 --> 31:01.580
Xiuyuan!

31:08.550 --> 31:10.660
It's a Fire-Releasing Pill. It neutralizes the Xuanhua Fire toxin.

31:20.550 --> 31:21.140
Feeling better?

31:21.470 --> 31:22.210
Feeling any better?

31:30.400 --> 31:32.250
We'll settle the score for knocking me out later.

31:33.120 --> 31:34.490
Now take me to the one who posed as me.

31:41.310 --> 31:41.940
Miaoqing!

31:43.200 --> 31:44.050
How did this happen?

31:47.070 --> 31:48.010
I failed to protect her.

31:49.200 --> 31:51.970
She was badly wounded by a demon spirit and Xuanhua Fire.

32:00.160 --> 32:01.490
Remember, don't open your eyes.

32:31.230 --> 32:33.770
I managed to protect her heart meridians, but...

32:41.120 --> 32:43.100
The Fire-Releasing Pill. Give it to her.

32:43.440 --> 32:46.620
Her soul has scattered. The pill won't work anymore.

32:49.790 --> 32:50.530
Let me try.

33:13.750 --> 33:14.730
Her soul is already lost.

33:15.990 --> 33:17.180
No amount of spirit power will help.

33:23.790 --> 33:25.420
But we can't just watch her die.

33:28.510 --> 33:29.660
I can call her soul back.

33:35.710 --> 33:36.770
Lifei, stay calm.

33:36.790 --> 33:37.940
Lu and I will help here.

33:38.120 --> 33:39.210
You go deal with the elders.

33:40.880 --> 33:41.380
Do you really have

33:41.400 --> 33:42.820
a way to bring her soul back?

33:44.790 --> 33:46.340
Many fishermen in the East Sea go out to sea.

33:46.880 --> 33:48.580
Strange things happen out there.

33:48.990 --> 33:50.530
It's not uncommon for souls to go missing out there.

33:51.360 --> 33:53.100
So there's an ancient soul-calling method in the East Sea.

33:54.990 --> 33:56.180
But this method

33:56.400 --> 33:57.580
comes with a strict condition.

33:58.200 --> 33:59.900
It requires the person who matters most to her

34:00.360 --> 34:01.620
to personally call out her name.

34:06.640 --> 34:07.210
I'll do it.

34:40.840 --> 34:41.420
Your Highness.

34:41.630 --> 34:42.170
Miaoqing.

34:43.590 --> 34:44.170
Miaoqing.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.300
Your Highness.

35:12.700 --> 35:13.170
This...

35:16.070 --> 35:16.860
What do we do?

35:17.550 --> 35:18.780
How do we ease her pain?

35:23.470 --> 35:27.050
Miaoqing, I'm here.

35:53.190 --> 35:54.090
Let me heal her.

35:55.470 --> 35:56.420
You may all leave.

36:05.470 --> 36:06.050
Let's go.

36:30.320 --> 36:30.970
Miaoqing.

36:40.880 --> 36:43.340
Miaoqing is truly devoted.

36:51.700 --> 36:52.900
Duanming City's situation is shifting.

36:53.220 --> 36:53.860
Return at once.

36:58.800 --> 37:00.650
Lifei, Duanming is unstable.

37:01.280 --> 37:03.050
Lu and I have to return to Wanxian Sect.

37:04.110 --> 37:06.450
Take care, everyone. Hope we meet again soon.

37:06.990 --> 37:07.700
You take care too.

37:26.060 --> 37:29.740
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

37:30.060 --> 37:32.560
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

37:33.920 --> 37:34.490
Lifei!

37:34.490 --> 37:36.340
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

37:36.580 --> 37:38.780
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

37:39.150 --> 37:40.610
Your spirit power isn't limitless.

37:41.150 --> 37:42.610
If you keep channeling it, you'll collapse.

37:44.020 --> 37:45.510
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

37:45.510 --> 37:47.340
Miaoqing ended up like this because of me.

37:48.760 --> 37:50.340
I'm the one Cuixuan was after...

37:50.360 --> 37:51.300
Jiang Lifei!

37:52.630 --> 37:54.130
You're just like me. Just an ordinary person.

37:54.150 --> 37:55.220
A mortal.

37:55.220 --> 37:56.880
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

37:56.880 --> 37:57.570
But...

37:58.590 --> 38:00.820
Whatever happened, it's in the past.

38:01.700 --> 38:02.340
Alright?

38:02.340 --> 38:04.040
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge. Past the pagoda♪

38:04.680 --> 38:06.960
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

38:07.760 --> 38:11.240
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

38:11.600 --> 38:13.880
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

38:14.400 --> 38:17.360
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

38:17.700 --> 38:18.740
Let's go back to Qingqiu together.

38:18.740 --> 38:20.280
♪Reign supreme♪

38:20.670 --> 38:21.900
We'll go somewhere no one can find us.

38:21.900 --> 38:23.590
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

38:23.590 --> 38:24.340
Just us.

38:34.550 --> 38:36.130
But I still haven't found my master.

38:37.110 --> 38:38.340
All this time,

38:38.990 --> 38:40.650
not a single word from him.

38:41.280 --> 38:43.010
And I don't know where Jiaping is.

38:43.150 --> 38:44.820
Let things take their course. Don't force it.

38:46.320 --> 38:48.340
Elder Chongyi meant the exact opposite of what he said.

38:48.360 --> 38:49.490
Don't you get it?

38:49.540 --> 38:51.890
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

38:51.890 --> 38:53.590
♪Yet I remain silent♪

38:53.590 --> 38:57.700
Lifei, listen to me. Go back to Qingqiu.

38:57.700 --> 38:59.210
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

38:59.370 --> 39:02.570
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

39:03.360 --> 39:05.260
Remember the first time we went back to Qingqiu?

39:06.960 --> 39:08.260
You said you wanted to build a big house.

39:09.990 --> 39:10.780
I've already planned it.

39:11.590 --> 39:13.740
A courtyard with rooms on all sides,

39:14.510 --> 39:15.340
filled with flowers

39:17.400 --> 39:18.570
blooming all year round.

39:20.040 --> 39:22.570
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

39:22.810 --> 39:26.670
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

39:26.670 --> 39:28.010
You said you love radishes.

39:29.030 --> 39:30.570
We'll plant radishes in the front and back yards.

39:30.570 --> 39:32.470
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

39:32.470 --> 39:33.090
Alright?

39:34.080 --> 39:36.360
♪Reign supreme♪

39:36.930 --> 39:40.890
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

39:41.920 --> 39:43.260
Besides radishes,

39:43.670 --> 39:45.530
we should keep some chickens and ducks too.

39:46.190 --> 39:47.530
With some meat,

39:47.800 --> 39:49.090
the stewed radish will taste better.

39:51.070 --> 39:51.820
Whatever you say.

39:51.820 --> 39:54.410
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

39:54.650 --> 39:57.770
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

39:57.810 --> 40:00.550
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

40:00.550 --> 40:03.010
With vegetables and meat, once we have it all set up,

40:03.320 --> 40:04.650
maybe my master will come back.

40:04.650 --> 40:08.570
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

40:16.480 --> 40:18.320
[Miniature Realm]

40:25.510 --> 40:28.860
You hid the Divine Tree by every means possible.

40:31.670 --> 40:33.530
But I still found it.

40:34.920 --> 40:35.700
Qingcheng,

40:37.360 --> 40:39.340
you lost after all.

40:41.470 --> 40:42.450
Let me see.

40:44.110 --> 40:44.900
Fine.

41:01.550 --> 41:02.050
You!

41:04.470 --> 41:05.940
What have you done?

41:08.550 --> 41:10.780
Things that shouldn't exist in this world.

41:12.220 --> 41:13.570
Better to destroy them.

41:45.360 --> 41:46.260
Qingcheng.

41:49.880 --> 41:51.420
You forced my hand.

41:54.840 --> 41:56.130
Gelin and Lu have returned to report.

41:57.030 --> 41:57.860
We should be going too.

42:00.840 --> 42:02.380
Tomorrow is Jingwu's coronation.

42:03.440 --> 42:04.380
Can you stay a little longer?

42:04.880 --> 42:05.860
If we stay,

42:05.990 --> 42:07.450
we might just cause you more trouble.

42:08.280 --> 42:10.570
You have to guide the Crown Prince and restore the Yue State.

42:10.880 --> 42:12.260
Don't wear yourself out for me.

42:13.150 --> 42:15.220
Next time we meet, I hope we're all doing well.

42:21.280 --> 42:22.050
Where are you going?

42:30.320 --> 42:31.260
We're going...

42:33.470 --> 42:35.650
Master is at Hushe Peak.

42:37.470 --> 42:38.780
Jiaping's distant-sensing talisman?

42:40.720 --> 42:41.740
He's in danger.

42:42.050 --> 42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.780 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
